<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>Dear Customer,</p>

    <p>
      Your bank statement for <strong><%= @statement.from_date %> to <%= @statement.to_date %></strong>
      for account <strong><%= @statement.account_number %></strong> has been generated successfully.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= @statement_url %>">Download Statement (PDF)</a>
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>PDF Password:</strong>
      Last 4 digits of the account number + first 4 characters of your email ID
      (e.g. Account: <code>6500000001</code>, Email: <code>dorji@gmail.com</code> → <code>0001dorj</code>)
    </p>

    <p>
      If you did not request this statement, please contact our support team (6070).
    </p>

    <p>
      Regards
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
